TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Simple Test for Heteroscedasticity and Random Coefficient Variation
AU  - Breusch, T. S.
AU  - Pagan, A. R.
AB  - [A simple test for heteroscedastic disturbances in a linear regression model is developed using the framework of the Lagrangian multiplier test. For a wide range of heteroscedastic and random coefficient specifications, the criterion is given as a readily computed function of the OLS residuals. Some finite sampleevidence is presented to supplement the general asymptotic properties of Lagrangian multiplier tests.]
